Remote Work Guidelines
 This policy outlines the guidelines and expectations for employees working remotely.
 Availability:- Employees must be available during core hours: 10:00 AM to 4:00 PM.
 Productivity:- Weekly check-ins with managers are mandatory.- Use Slack and Zoom for all communications.
 Security:- Use VPN and avoid public Wi-Fi for accessing company systems.- Do not share company devices with others at home.
 For remote work issues, contact remotework@company.com.
